<SYNC Start=1221408><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1225357><P Class=ENCC>
Hey, he's not crying!
<SYNC Start=1227689><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1231496><P Class=ENCC>
Hey, he's not crying!
<SYNC Start=1233930><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1239938><P Class=ENCC>
There's still pie!
<SYNC Start=1242031><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1242975><P Class=ENCC>
I'm here. I'm here.
<SYNC Start=1245205><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1245944><P Class=ENCC>
How's my little boy?
<SYNC Start=1247935><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1248380><P Class=ENCC>
You want Daddy to change<br>your diaper? I know, I know.
<SYNC Start=1252510><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1253385><P Class=ENCC>
