Hey, I have a question.
<SYNC Start=1269797><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1272371><P Class=ENCC>
How come it says,<br>"Property of Human Services"?
<SYNC Start=1275397><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1280412><P Class=ENCC>
You are gonna love this.
<SYNC Start=1282903><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1283749><P Class=ENCC>
Can you hold Ben for a sec?
<SYNC Start=1285239><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1286151><P Class=ENCC>
Come here. Come here.
<SYNC Start=1287083><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1287352><P Class=ENCC>
Stay back! I've got kiwi!<br>Run, Joey, run!
<SYNC Start=1290412><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1296161><P Class=ENCC>
Smelly cat, smelly cat
<SYNC Start=1299494><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1299731><P Class=ENCC>
What are they feeding you?
<SYNC Start=1301824><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1302634><P Class=ENCC>
No, no. I'm sorry, it's:
<SYNC Start=1303623><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1303835><P Class=ENCC>
Smelly cat, smelly cat
<SYNC Start=1306998><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1311410><P Class=ENCC>
Smelly cat, smelly cat
<SYNC Start=1315107><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1315747><P Class=ENCC>
Better!
<SYNC Start=1316771><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1316982><P Class=ENCC>
Much better. Good.
<SYNC Start=1318074><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1318283><P Class=ENCC>
Don't feel bad,<br>because it's a hard song.
<SYNC Start=1320945><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1323188><P Class=ENCC>
-You want to try it again?<br>-From the top?
<SYNC Start=1325588><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1325791><P Class=ENCC>
There is no "top," all right?
<SYNC Start=1328419><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1329094><P Class=ENCC>
That's the beauty of "Smelly Cat."
<SYNC Start=1331187><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1334466><P Class=ENCC>
Why don't you just follow me.
<SYNC Start=1336331><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1337502><P Class=ENCC>
Smelly cat, smelly cat
<SYNC Start=1341097><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1341340><P Class=ENCC>
What are they feeding you?
<SYNC Start=1344138><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1344710><P Class=ENCC>
Smelly cat, smelly cat
